             was indicted for <rs id="t18150510-12-off67" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150510-12-off67" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150510-12-off67" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18150510-12-cd68" type="crimeDate">28th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150510-12-off67 t18150510-12-cd68"></join>, nine pounds weight of white pepper, value 27 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18150510-12-victim171" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Ryde
                  <interp inst="t18150510-12-victim171" type="surname" value="Ryde"></interp>
